thread.title: Jim Rinke

author: Jim Rinke
title: Jim Rinke
text: I'm always pleased when a vendor provides exactly the product or service they advertise. Antonio was very helpful. Even though rushmypassport facilitates, you are still dealing with a government process, so there are a lot of pieces and parts. I had to call and ask questions a couple of times and they were very helpful. In the end, I received my passport 1 day before the promise date. Great Job!
